Comment.MultiLanguageText: Send max value out to drill recorder

AttributeList.Text: Hard coded rollover value to match encoder rollver value from TM Count card
Differential Pressure x torque factor(ft-lbs/psi) unless bypass running * efficiency. Use raw reading value and filter after

Drill torque setpoint cannot be greater than 0.95 % of the makeup setpoint MU Torque always low speed as it cannot shift Drill torque depends on speed settings MU threshold is a percent of setpoint Add 500 PSI to setpoint to overcome charge pressure
These setpoints are based on a percent of the user input
If System on then record max if current temp greater than max REset max if system off and PTO pressed
If System is off Set values to 0, unless PTO is pressed then send full signal for 8 minutes while off. While system enabled send actual values
